&lt;p&gt;• Define the service model, standards, and patient experience philosophy that Directors and their teams operationalize&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Anticipate shifts across the PBM, payer, and healthcare landscape — regulatory, competitive, and clinical — and position the function to lead through them&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Serve as the executive voice of the patient internally, ensuring patient needs are represented in product, clinical, commercial, and operational decisions&lt;/p&gt;
